com.bitwise.decaf.editor.grammar
Interface Phrase.TypeChameleon

Enclosing interface:
Phrase
public static interface Phrase.TypeChameleon

Instances of Grammar.Content may additionally implement TypeChameleon if their content can be converted to other (most often primitive) types. When an expected type is applied to this Phrase, it will pass that type to its content with applyType(Type) iff it implements TypeChalemeon; otherwise the expectedType will be ignored.
